<sec id="id-f6dc66d1-7298-4616-c292-7d8b6777d180"><title><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="46cd555a-b16e-414f-b633-640043aa541d" timestamp="1667476835250"?>Example of a national "Professional equality index"<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="46cd555a-b16e-414f-b633-640043aa541d"?></title><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="ed663757-7f15-4ff9-82ce-fe432733b76a" text="[Former Box 4]" timestamp="1675426670948"?><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="0edc6983-a188-46cf-e4dd-d4ed11f0fae7" timestamp="1667476827332"?>For example, all French companies<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0edc6983-a188-46cf-e4dd-d4ed11f0fae7"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="6e20e040-dfd3-4c08-d6cf-aec5af5b9604" timestamp="1671529550396"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="6e20e040-dfd3-4c08-d6cf-aec5af5b9604"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="6e9a4e22-f011-413f-d41d-eff898db9304" text="Companies " timestamp="1671529552161"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="6bdc6e83-df59-41f1-bce2-2882cc579305" timestamp="1667476827332"?>with at least 50 employee should calculate and publish their professional gender equality index every year. This national "100-points professional equality index" is calculated according to four or five indicators (depending on whether the company has more or fewer than 250 employees):<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="6bdc6e83-df59-41f1-bce2-2882cc579305"?></p><list list-type="dash"><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="8effadb3-6489-4932-8866-b25a0feb3d4a" timestamp="1667476827332"?><list-item id="id-2f1375fb-a35f-407a-99b2-47cf0d74dd36"><p>the pay gap between <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="8effadb3-6489-4932-8866-b25a0feb3d4a"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="ca31a1ed-d2a7-4e56-e360-d4ad83c050a7" timestamp="1669040090321"?>wo<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ca31a1ed-d2a7-4e56-e360-d4ad83c050a7"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="76ccc729-7da5-4a3e-f81e-b85e98f3668c" timestamp="1667476827332"?>men and<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="76ccc729-7da5-4a3e-f81e-b85e98f3668c"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="27f3426f-d67c-4935-c378-f19202a019ad" text=" w" timestamp="1669040092311"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="34a2b519-c118-46c5-f438-03ec99d03fb9" timestamp="1669040093699"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="34a2b519-c118-46c5-f438-03ec99d03fb9"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="ce59f412-6007-4245-c347-1f70d660dedb" text="o" timestamp="1669040094375"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="5ac30d6a-f6b0-4102-fa4e-e13f40fcb226" timestamp="1667476827332"?>men;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-baf14f5c-bb34-450a-b8a6-8962fbf8fab4"><p>the difference in the breakdown of individual pay rises;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-507474e6-1960-401b-9f7d-da5e562313ca"><p>the difference in the breakdown of promotions (only in companies with more than 250 employees);</p></list-item><list-item id="id-0a43ef53-db61-4b4f-9fcd-1d71f2c1c19b"><p>the number of female employees who receive a pay rise on their return from maternity leave;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-14fdd439-e82a-4813-f072-78b83b01a666"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5ac30d6a-f6b0-4102-fa4e-e13f40fcb226"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="18a685b4-e1d3-4a04-f542-dfb8074e1d01" timestamp="1668691232761"?>Gender <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="18a685b4-e1d3-4a04-f542-dfb8074e1d01"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="5d0eced0-17e0-42de-c9d7-1df3fc516872" timestamp="1667476827332"?>parity amongst the 10 highest-paid employees</p></list-item><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5d0eced0-17e0-42de-c9d7-1df3fc516872"?></list><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="a1747009-41a1-4250-ceee-6d0636b589bc" timestamp="1667476827332"?>If the index is below 75 points, the company is required to take corrective measures to achieve a score of at least 75 points within three years.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a1747009-41a1-4250-ceee-6d0636b589bc"?></p><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="4681f64c-4452-428a-91e9-a4adb3aa4a9c" text="+ add origin of this example ? See with ISO CS editor][" timestamp="1675426695194"?><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="e382442c-ac85-44d4-ec69-b38582fdf922" timestamp="1667476827332"?>The number of cases of discrimination and labo<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="e382442c-ac85-44d4-ec69-b38582fdf922"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="ced65194-6046-4526-b1c1-05e87c7b0f2d" timestamp="1674567803658"?>u<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ced65194-6046-4526-b1c1-05e87c7b0f2d"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="7f1b1226-01d8-4ddb-de28-df39c868b093" timestamp="1667476827332"?>r violence sanctioned with respect to those reported could also be an interesting indicator.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7f1b1226-01d8-4ddb-de28-df39c868b093"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="7afcabfa-0fa1-44a7-f8f3-f966aa158228" timestamp="1675426714044"?>Other countries may have similar gender pay reporting processes.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7afcabfa-0fa1-44a7-f8f3-f966aa158228"?></p></sec>